le%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20clips%2C%20allegedly%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20a%20day%20after%20he%20voted%20on%20April%2026%20in%20Phase%202%20of%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20-%20grandson%20of%20JDS%20chief%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20-%20has%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint%20claiming%20that%20the%20videos%20being%20circulated%20are%20doctored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20formed%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20look%20into%20the%20obscene%20videos%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20the%20SIT%20came%20after%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%20recommended%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20Accused%20Of%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scandal%20involves%20explicit%20videos%20that%20were%20allegedly%20shot%20by%20the%20MP%20and%20were%20circulated%20widely%20in%20the%20Hassan%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20up%20by%20a%20woman%20filing%20a%20police%20case%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20She%20alleged%20she%20had%20been%20sexually%20abused%20multiple%20times%20between%202019%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20also%20claimed%20that%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20misbehaved%20with%20her%20daughter%20over%20a%20video%20call%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20Prajwal's%20father%20HD%20Revanna%20also%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20when%20his%20wife%20was%20not%20at%20home.%C2%A0She%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20her%20life%20as%20well%20as%20other%20members%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Leader%20Devaraje%20Gowda%2C%20who%20was%20the%20party's%20Holenarsipura%20candidate%20during%20the%202023%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20had%20written%20to%20then%20state%20president%20BY%20Vijayendra%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20flagging%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20allegations%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20family%2C%20including%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20received%20a%20pen%20drive%20containing%202%2C976%20explicit%20videos%20of%20women%20-%20which%20were%20then%20being%20used%20to%20blackmail%20them%20into%20continuing%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20activities.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20align%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20and%20if%20we%20nominate%20a%20JD(S)%20candidate%20in%20Hassan%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20these%20videos%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20brahmastra%20and%20we%20will%20be%20tainted%20as%20a%20party%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20family%20of%20a%20rapist.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20image%20of%20our%20party%20nationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Devaraje%20Gowdahad%20written%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20And%20What%20He%20Says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20H%20D%20Devegowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20is%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20candidate%20in%20the%20Hassan%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20where%20voting%20was%20held%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20April%2026.%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20or%20JD(S)%2C%20joined%20the%20NDA%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20left%20for%20Germany%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20videos%20emerged%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20claiming%20the%20videos%20were%20doctored%20and%20they%20were%20being%20circulated%20to%20%26quot%3Btarnish%20his%20image%20and%20poison%20voters'%20minds%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal's%20father%20HD%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20filed%20by%20their%20former%20house%20help%2C%20is%20MLA%20from%20Holenarasipur%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESex%20Scandal%20Sparks%20Political%20Slugfest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20has%20also%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20squabble%20between%20the%20JDS%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20amid%20the%20controversy%20around%20his%20purported%20sex%20tapes.%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20as%20a%20party%2C%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20videos%20and%20neither%20do%20we%20have%20any%20comments%20to%20make%20on%20the%20SIT%20probe%20announced%20by%20the%20state%20government%20into%20the%20alleged%20sex%20scandal%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20state%20spokesperson%20S%20Prakash%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20's%20uncle%20and%20JD(S)%20leader%20H%20D%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20he%20would%20like%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20facts%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20scandal%20involving%20his%20nephew%2C%20but%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20forgiving%20anyone%20who%20has%20committed%20a%20crime%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20JD(S)%20leader%2C%20Sharangouda%20Kandkur%20has%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%20In%20a%20two-page%20letter%20made%20public%20Monday%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Kandkur%20told%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20the%20JDS%20had%20been%20left%20%26quot%3Bembarrassed%20by%20the%20circulating%20videos%2C%20and%20it%20damages%20the%20reputation%20of%20both%20you%20and%20your%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20party%20helped%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20flee%20the%20country%20amid%20row%20over%20alleged%20sex%20clips%20involving%20him.%C2%A0Congress%20leaders%20an