A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-take-decision-on-hindustan-zinc-ofs-after-testing-mkt-mines-secy-124042900462_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-take-decision-on-hindustan-zinc-ofs-after-testing-mkt-mines-secy-124042900462_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-take-decision-on-hindustan-zinc-ofs-after-testing-mkt-mines-secy-124042900462_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won%20World%20Cup%20With%20India%2C%20Former%20Coach%20Explains%20Decision%20To%20Join%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20made%20a%20significant%20move%20on%20Sunday%20as%20they%20announced%20the%20appointment%20of%20World%20Cup-winning%20Gary%20Kirsten%20as%20their%20head%20coach%20for%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is%2C%20while%20former%20Australian%20pacer%20Jason%20Gillespie%20will%20take%20over%20that%20role%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Kirsten%20has%20had%20successful%20stints%20with%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20before%2C%20with%20his%202011%20OD%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20with%20the%20MS%20Dhoni-led%20side%20arguably%20being%20the%20highlight.%20Along%20with%20them%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20all-rounder%20Azhar%20Mahmood%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20coach%20of%20the%20team%20across%20the%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20his%20decision%20to%20coach%20the%20Pakistan%20team%2C%20Kirsten%20said%20that%20his%20primary%20aim%20remains%20to%20unite%20the%20Pakistan%20white-ball%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tremendous%20honour%20to%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20coaching%20the%20Pakistan%20men's%20national%20team%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%20and%20to%20rejoin%20the%20international%20cricket%20arena%20after%20some%20time.%20I%20eagerly%20anticipate%20this%20opportunity%20and%20aim%20to%20contribute%20positively%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20men's%20national%20team%20in%20limited-overs%20cricket.%20Kirsten's%20strategy%20focuses%20on%20prioritizing%20continuity%20in%20team%20selections%2C%20aiming%20to%20create%20a%20stable%20and%20consistent%20environment%20that%20allows%20players%20to%20perform%20at%20their%20best.%20He%20believes%20that%20maintaining%20a%20cohesive%20unit%20and%20building%20strong%20team%20dynamics%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20team's%20success%20in%20international%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20beautiful%20aspects%20of%20cricket%20is%20its%20universality.%20Across%20cultures%2C%20there's%20a%20shared%20understanding%20when%20we%20discuss%20the%20game.%20My%20goal%20is%20to%20unite%20the%20Pakistan%20men's%20white-ball%20team%2C%20harnessing%20their%20considerable%20talents%20towards%20a%20common%20objective%2C%20and%20achieving%20success%20together%20on%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirsten%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20mentor%20of%20IPL%20side%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20over%20from%20Pakistan's%20tour%20of%20England%20from%20May%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20play%20four%20T20Is%20and%20from%20there%20the%20team%20will%20travel%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%20been%20on%20the%20search%20for%20a%20full-time%20head%20coach%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20where%20they%20failed%20to%20enter%20the%20knockout%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20shambolic%20effort%20in%20the%20marquee%20event%20held%20in%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20sacked%20the%20entire%20set%20of%20coaching%20staff%20%E2%80%93%20head%20coach%20Grant%20Bradburn%2C%20team%20director%20Mickey%20Arthur%2C%20bowling%20coach%20Morne%20Morkel%20and%20batting%20coach%20Andrew%20Puttick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremier%20batter%20Babar%20Azam%20was%20also%20removed%20from%20captaincy%20post%20the%20ICC%20showpiece%20with%20Pakistan%20opting%20to%20appoint%20pacer%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20as%20their%20white-ball%20leader%20and%20Shan%20Masood%20doing%20that%20duty%20in%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20that%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20also%20turned%20to%20former%20cricketer%20Muhammad%20Hafeez%20for%20the%20guiding%20role%20during%20their%20tour%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hafeez%20lost%20the%20job%20after%20Pakistan%20lost%200-3%20in%20the%20Test%20series%20and%201-4%20in%20the%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Masood%20was%20retained%20as%20Test%20captain%2C%20Afridi%20was%20relieved%20from%20leadership%20and%20Babar%20was%20reinstated%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pakistan%20could%20not%20find%20a%20full-time%20head%20coach%20despite%20them%20approaching%20some%20top%20names%20such%20Matthew%20Hayden%20and%20Shane%20Watson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20they%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Kirsten%2C%20who%20had%20led%20India%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20in%202011%2C%20and%20Gillespie%2C%20who%20comes%20with%20a%20bagful%20of%20coaching%20experience%20with%20English%20county%20side%20Sussex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714383060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ftg0vlnm_gary-kirsten-bcci_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fformer-india-coach-gary-kirsten-opens-up-on-decision-to-join-pakistan-team-5542114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gary%20Kirsten%20was%20Team%20India's%20head%20coach%20when%20MS%20Dhoni's%20side%20won%20the%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22173kg%20of%20drugs%20seized%20off%20west%20coast%2C%202%20held%22%2C%22content%