re-planned-a-move-to-compensate-nawaz-sharif%2Famp_articleshow%2F109689461.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%2C%20JDS%20In%20Firefighting%20Mode%20Over%20Deve%20Gowda's%20Grandson's%20Sex%20Scandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJanata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20lawmaker%20Sharangouda%20Kandkur%20has%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20party%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2FPrajwal-Revanna%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20explicit%20videos%20-%20allegedly%20showing%20the%20Hassan%20MP%20sexually%20assaulting%20multiple%20women%20-%20that%20began%20circulating%20a%20day%20after%20voting%20in%20his%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20two-page%20letter%20made%20public%20Monday%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Kandkur%20told%20party%20patriarch%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20the%20JDS%20had%20been%20left%20%26quot%3Bembarrassed%20by%20the%20circulating%20videos%2C%20and%20it%20damages%20the%20reputation%20of%20both%20you%20and%20your%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna%20-%20who%20is%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda's%20grandson%20-%20is%20not%20currently%20in%20India.%20He%20left%20for%20Germany%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20videos%20emerged%20online.%20On%20Sunday%20he%20f%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-poison-voters-deve-gowda-grandson-prajwal-revanna-on-morphed-sex-videos-5540960%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiled%20a%20police%20complaint%20claiming%20the%20clips%20-%20there%20are%20reportedly%20thousands%20-%20were%20doctored%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20videos%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20were%20being%20distributed%20to%20%26quot%3Btarnish%20his%20image%20and%20poison%20voters'%20minds%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20a%20special%20team%20had%20been%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-sets-up-team-to-probe-sex-scandal-involving-jds-mp-5538419%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESiddaramaiah%20Sets%20Up%20Team%20To%20Probe%20Sex%20Scandal%20Involving%20JDS%20MP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%2C%20which%20has%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sha%20election%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20comment%20pending%20a%20complete%20inquiry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20-%20who%20is%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda's%20son%20-%20said%20there%20could%20be%20no%20question%20of%20forgiving%20anyone%20who%20had%20committed%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flet-facts-come-out-hd-kumaraswamy-on-sex-scandal-involving-his-nephew-prajwal-revanna-5541796%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLet%20Facts%20Come%20Out%26quot%3B%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20On%20Nephew's%20Sex%20Scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20party%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Mr%20Revanna%20apparently%20fleeing%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIf%20he%20has%20gone%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%20getting%20him%20back%20is%20their%20(the%20special%20investigative%20team)%20responsibility.%20What%20should%20I%20say...%20SIT%20will%20get%20him%2C%20don't%20worry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scandal%20broke%20last%20week%20after%20a%20woman%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20against%20Mr%20Revanna%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20she%20had%20been%20sexually%20abused%20multiple%20times%20between%202019%20and%202022.%20The%20clips%20circulating%20show%20more%20women%20and%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20forward%20to%20file%20cases%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20has%20also%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20squabble%20between%20the%20JDS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20national%20party's%20leaders%20distancing%20themselves%20from%20the%20state%20party%20and%20calling%20for%20a%20rethink.%20S%20Prakash%2C%20the%20BJP%20state%20unit's%20chief%20spokesperson%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20as%20a%20party%2C%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20videos%20and%20neither%20do%20we%20have%20any%20comments%20to%20make...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20also%20gotten%20involved%2C%20after%20reports%20some%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20told%20their%20party's%20state%20boss%2C%20BY%20Vijayendra%2C%20of%20the%20clips%20back%20in%20December.%20They%20have%20questioned%20their%20rival's%20decision%20to%20field%20Mr%20Revanna%20despite%20knowledge%20of%20the%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20leader%20with%20whom%20the%20PM%20gets%20photographed%20by%20placing%20his%20hand%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20The%20leader%20for%20whom%20the%20PM%20himself%20campaigned%2010%20days%20ago.%20Praised%20him%20on%20stage.%20Today%2C%20that%20leader%20of%20Karnataka%20is%20absconding%20from%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourteen%20of%20Karnataka's%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20including%20Hassan%2C%20voted%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20last%20week.%20The%20remaining%2014%20are%20due%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207%2C%20but%20the%20JDS%20is%20not%20contesting%20any%20of%20these%20seats.%20As%20per%20the%20seat-share%20agreement%2C%20the%20party%20-%20which%20broke%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20in%20October%20-%20fought%20only%20three%20in%20south%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714382640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2