20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20identity%20and%20income.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20got%20started%20with%20online%20focus%20groups%20back%20in%202020.%20A%20friend%20posted%20an%20Instagram%20story%20about%20how%20research%20participants%20were%20needed%20for%20a%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was%2C%20but%20I%20clicked%20on%20the%20link%20and%20filled%20out%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%20I%20make%20between%20%242%2C000%20and%20%243%2C000%20each%20month%20participating%20in%20focus%20groups.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20I've%20made%20an%20average%20of%20%242%2C845%20a%20month.%20I%20then%20created%20my%20own%20business%2C%20teaching%20others%20how%20to%20make%20money%20from%20focus%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20wondered%20why%20I%20would%20be%20paid%20to%20share%20my%20opinion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20days%20after%20I%20filled%20out%20that%20initial%20survey%20in%202020%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20a%20recruiter.%20She%20confirmed%20my%20answers%20and%20told%20me%20a%20little%20more%20about%20what%20the%20research%20study%20was.%20It%20was%20going%20to%20be%20about%20social%20media%2C%20and%20I%20would%20be%20paid%20%24175%20for%20spending%2090%20minutes%20on%20a%20Zoom%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20me%2C%20four%20other%20participants%2C%20and%20a%20moderator.%20The%20conversation%20just%20flew%20by%2C%20and%20it%20honestly%20felt%20like%20just%20a%20normal%20chat%20geared%20toward%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20check%20in%20the%20mail%20for%20%24175%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20so%20this%20was%20legit!%26quot%3B%20While%20it%20didn't%20necessarily%20sound%20like%20a%20scam%2C%20I%20wondered%20how%20and%20why%20I%20would%20get%20paid%20to%20do%20something%20as%20fun%20as%20sharing%20my%20opinion%20on%20a%20specific%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20quit%20my%20retail%20job%20in%20search%20of%20more%20flexibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20store%20manager.%20I%20had%20a%20decent%20job%20with%20benefits%20and%20stability%2C%20but%20the%20work%20had%20started%20to%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20my%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20more%20flexibility%20and%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20on%20a%20leave%20of%20absence%20and%20started%20to%20search%20online%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20money%20through%20side%20hustles.%20I%20got%20back%20into%20doing%20focus%20groups%20and%20started%20applying%20to%20new%20studies.%20I%20came%20across%20a%20course%20on%20YouTube%20that%20was%20very%20good%20at%20teaching%20me%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20participating%20in%20research%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20also%20tried%20other%20side%20hustles%20like%20e-commerce%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20Shipt%2C%20they%20didn't%20feel%20as%20worth%20it.%20I%20noticed%20that%20I%20was%20consistently%20bringing%20in%20%242%2C000%20to%20%243%2C000%20a%20month%20from%20focus%20groups%20alone%2C%20so%20I%20eventually%20transitioned%20to%20concentrate%20solely%20on%20doing%20focus%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20made%20over%20%242%2C500%20working%20only%2033%20hours%20in%20a%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20I%20participated%20in%2028%20focus%20groups%20for%20a%20total%20of%201%2C195%20minutes%20or%20around%2020%20hours.%20I%20tend%20to%20spend%20about%2035%20minutes%20per%20day%2C%20Monday%20through%20Friday%2C%20just%20applying%20to%20focus%20groups.%20In%20those%2035%20minutes%2C%20I%20can%20usually%20apply%20to%2010%20to%2015%20focus%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20I%20spent%202%2C000%20minutes%2C%20or%20about%2033%20hours%2C%20applying%20for%20focus%20groups%20and%20participating%20in%20them.%20Despite%20working%20far%20less%20than%20full-time%20hours%2C%20I%20made%20%242%2C568%20from%20these%20focus%20groups%2C%20or%20about%20%2477%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20in%20March%2C%20I%20participated%20in%2018%20focus%20groups%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%242%2C770%20or%20an%20average%20of%20%24154%20per%20focus%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20focus%20groups%2C%20you%20can%20get%20paid%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways.%20I've%20gotten%20paid%20through%20virtual%20Visa%20gift%20cards%2C%20direct%20deposits%2C%20in-person%20checks%2C%20cash%2C%20PayPal%2C%20checks%20in%20the%20mail%2C%20Zelle%2C%20and%20Amazon%20gift%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stack%20of%20about%20a%20dozen%20Visa%20gift%20cards%20on%20a%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662aabcc23b29110d3032a1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20many%20gift%20cards%20Filipe%20has%20received%20as%20compensation.%3Cp%3EFilipe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20keep%20track%20of%20it%20all%20in%20a%20spreadsheet%20that%20I%20created%2C%20and%20that%20really%20helps%20me%20visualize%20how%20much%20I'm%20making%20every%20single%20month%20and%20make%20my%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Filipe's%20spreadsheet%20he%20uses%20to%20track%20the%20focus%20groups%20he%20applies%20to%20and%20participates%20in.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662aabf810dfcda4096379d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFilipe%20uses%20a%20spreadsheet%20to%20carefully%20track%20where%20and%20how%20much%20money%20he's%20made.%3Cp%3EFilipe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20focus%20groups%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFocus%20groups%20are%20consumer%20studies%20by%20big%20brands%20(like%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Chase%2C%20and%20Facebook)%20who%20want%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20their%20ad%2C%20service%2C%20or%20product%20will%20resonate%20with%20the%20consumer%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they'll%20pay%20big%20money%20for%20your%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20organize%20one-on-one%20or%20group%20interviews%20that%20vary%20in%20length.%20Some%20might%20take%20a%20full%20day%2C%20while%20others%20are%2090%20minutes.%20Some%20of%20the%20shortest%20ones%20are%20just%2010%20or%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20really%20varies%2C%20but%20the%20average%20pay%20rate%20is%2090%20minutes%20for%20%24150.%20The%20benchmark%20I%20set%20to%20decide%20whether%20a%20focus%20group%20is%20worth%20participating%20in%20is%20generally%20at%20least%20%2450%20for%2030%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20specialized%20research%20studies%20that%20pay%20even%20more%2C%20which%20look%20for%20people%20working%20in%20specific%20fields%2C%20such%20as%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20dentists.%20One%20of%20my%20friends%20in%20Texas%20is%20a%20dentist%2C%20and%20he%20found%20a%20focus%20group%20that%20paid%20%24260%20for%20an%20hour%20of%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQualifying%20for%20a%20focus%20group%20is%20a%20numbers%20game.%20The%20more%20applications%20you%20fill%20out%2C%20the%20more%20you'll%20book.%20It's%20almost%20like%20applying%20to%20jobs%3B%20it's%20probably%20not%20as%20competitive%20as%20job%20applications%2C%20but%20the%20same%20idea%20applies%20%E2%80%94%20you%20need%20to%20apply%20to%20a%20lot%20to%20get%20into%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20applications%20are%20really%20easy%20to%20complete%20and%20only%20take%20a%20minute%20or%20two%2C%20while%20others%20take%20five%20or%2C%20at%20most%2C%2010%20minutes%20to%20fill%20out.%20They%20ask%20demographic%20questions%20tailored%20to%20a%20specific%20focus%20group%2C%20as%20well%20as%20which%20products%20and%20services%20you%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20focus%20group%20is%20a%20very%20moderated%20conversation.%20Whether%20you're%20in%20a%20group%20or%20a%20one-on-one%20call%2C%20a%20moderator%20asks%20you%20questions%20and%20makes%20sure%20that%20everyone%20feels%20comfortable.%20They%20guide%20the%20conversations%20in%20the%20way%20that%20their%20client%20(the%20big%20company)%20wants%20the%20conversations%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20first%2030%20minutes%20are%20questions%20that%20help%20them%20understand%20who%20you%20are%20and%20what%20you%20like%20to%20do.%20Then%2C%20they%20start%20to%20guide%20the%20conversation%20over%20to%20the%20main%20topic.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20show%20you%20ads%20or%20ad%20concepts%20and%20ask%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20them.%20It's%20standard%20to%20sign%20an%20NDA%20because%20you'll%20be%20seeing%20ads%20for%20products%20or%20services%20that%20haven't%20been%20released%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20coolest%20focus%20groups%20I've%20done%20was%20a%20four-part%20study%20on%20food.%20While%20I%20can't%20say%20specifics%2C%20the%20first%20three%20parts%20were%20questions%20about%20food%2C%20and%20the%20fourth%20and%20final%20part%20involved%20a%20trip%20to%20Chicago%20that%20was%20entirely%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20huge%20foodie%2C%20and%20I%20love%20Chicago%3B%20it's%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20cities%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20food.%20The%20focus%20group%20in%20Chicago%20was%20a%20four-hour%20in-person%20group%20with%20other%20study%20participants.%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Selfie%20of%20Filipe%20crossing%20a%20bridge%20on%20the%20Chicago%20River%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662aac710dfb1341e9ff49a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFilipe%20walking%20to%20his%20hotel%20in%20Chicago's%20River%20North%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3EFilipe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIf%20you're%20consistent%2C%20you%20could%20make%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%2C%20I%20was%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20searching%20for%20good%20focus%20groups.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20websites%20that%20offer%20low-paying%20surveys%2C%20so%20those%20are%20very%20common%20to%20find%2C%20but%20actual%20focus%20groups%20that%20pay%20more%20are%20much%20harder%20to%20find.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20searching%20throughout%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20to%20find%20these%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20free%20ways%20to%20find%20focus%20groups%20are%20by%20searching%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20groups%20near%20me%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Btaste%20tests%20near%20me%26quot%3B%20on%20Google%2C%20Craigslist%2C%20and%20social%20media.%20It's%20important%20to%20beware%20of%20potential%20scams%2C%20though.%20Avoid%20applying%20to%20surveys%20found%20on%20those%20sites%20if%20they%20don't%20share%20the%20incentive%20amount%20or%20if%20the%20amount%20is%20oddly%20high%2C%20like%20%24750%20for%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20biggest%20tips%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20get%20started%20on%20focus%20groups%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApply%20to%2010-15%20surveys%20per%20day%20and%20stay%20consistent!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20a%20numbers%20game%2C%20and%20so%20the%20more%20surveys%20you%20fill%20out%2C%20the%20more%20you're%20going%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20get%20discouraged%20if%20you%20fill%20out%20a%20bunch%20of%20applications%20and%20don't%20hear%20back.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20will%20not%20book%20every%20single%20group.%20Each%20focus%20group%20has%20a%20specific%20criteria%20and%20quota%20to%20fill%2C%20and%20it%20can%20take%20weeks%20to%20get%20a%20response.%20Just%20keep%20at%20it%3B%20they're%20going%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20organized.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20you%20start%20getting%20booked%2C%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20dates%20of%20the%20studies%20in%20a%20spreadsheet%20so%20you%20don't%20miss%20them%2C%20and%20note%20when%20the%20payment%20is%20meant%20to%20come%20in.%20I%20actually%20caught%20a%20few%20instances%20where%20companies%20forgot%20to%20pay%20me%20for%20studies%20I%20had%20completed%20several%20months%20prior.%20They%20were%20reputable%20companies%20with%20a%20huge%20volume%20of%20focus%20groups%2C%20so%20things%20probably%20slipped%20through%20the%20cracks.%20Each%20time%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20company%2C%20and%20they%20promptly%20paid%20me%20what%20I%20was%20owed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20stay%20consistent%20and%20put%20in%20an%20hour%20a%20day%20just%20to%20apply%20and%20participate%20in%20focus%20groups%2C%20you%20could%20walk%20away%20with%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%20I%20know%20people%20who%20do%20this%20part-time%20while%20working%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20and%20they're%20making%20%241%2C000%20to%20%242%2C000%20consistently%2C%20month%20after%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20an%20interesting%20side%20hustle%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Jane%20Zhang%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajanezhang%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejanezhang%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffocus-group-side-hustle-sharing-opinion-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714381921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662ab7f123b29110d3034071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffocus-group-side-hustle-sharing-opinion-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2030-year-old%20makes%20between%20%242%2C000%20and%20%243%2C000%20a%20month%20from%20focus%20groups.%20Here's%20how.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22janezhang%40insider.com%20(Jane%20Zhang)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl