0care.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20working%20full-time%20at%20GreenPal%2C%20I%20spent%20nine%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-remote-workers-promotion-return-office-push-flexible-work-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20Dell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20first%20held%20a%20sales%20role.%20Five%20years%20in%2C%20I%20transitioned%20into%20a%20management%20role%2C%20where%20I%20stayed%20until%202017.%20I%20learned%20invaluable%20lessons%20in%20leadership%2C%20strategic%20planning%2C%20and%20team%20management%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20been%20crucial%20in%20steering%20GreenPal%20toward%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20left%20my%20stable%20job%20at%20Dell%20to%20find%20a%20more%20meaningful%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20six-figure%20salary%20and%20was%20comfortable%20at%20Dell%2C%20but%20launching%20GreenPal%20was%20fueled%20by%20a%20quest%20for%20greater%20purpose.%20I%20was%20driven%20by%20the%20urge%20to%20solve%20a%20common%20problem.%20This%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburned-out-entrepreneur-business-retreat-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eventure%20into%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20just%20a%20career%20change%20but%20a%20commitment%20to%20innovating%20how%20lawn%20care%20services%20are%20accessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancing%20GreenPal's%20inception%20demanded%20significant%20personal%20sacrifices.%20Because%20of%20my%20belief%20in%20GreenPal%2C%20I%20sold%20my%20house%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcash-out-retirement-401k-savings-when-switching-jobs-unemployment-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashed%20out%20my%20401(k)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20make%20this%20work%2C%20I%20moved%20home%20with%20my%20mom%20for%20a%20year%2C%20which%20was%20humbling%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20right%20choice.%20I%20then%20got%20a%20small%20apartment%20with%20Bryan.%3C%2Fp%3E