0to%20deliver%20a%20product%20that%20met%20our%20specifications%20and%20went%20out%20of%20business%20shortly%20after.%20This%20left%20us%20without%20a%20functional%20website%20and%20with%20no%20recourse%20to%20recover%20our%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setback%20delayed%20our%20market%20entry%20and%20forced%20us%20to%20reconsider%20our%20strategy.%20This%20experience%20taught%20us%20a%20crucial%20lesson%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20technical%20expertise%20within%20our%20founding%20team.%20My%20other%20cofounder%2C%20Zach%20Hendrix%2C%20went%20to%20Nashville%20Software%20School%20and%20learned%20how%20to%20build%20the%20current%20website%20and%20apps%20we%20use%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20absolutely%20do%20not%20miss%20my%209-5%20at%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20piece%20of%20advice%20I'd%20share%20with%20other%20entrepreneurs%20is%20to%20brace%20yourself%20for%20a%20ride%20that%20can%20be%20lonely%20and%20seemingly%20without%20reward%20for%20a%20long%20stretch.%20Success%20in%20entrepreneurship%20often%20comes%20after%20enduring%20periods%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20solitude.%20Stay%20resilient%20and%20keep%20pushing%20forward%2C%20even%20when%20the%20immediate%20outcomes%20aren't%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20consider%20myself%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20but%20I%20will%20never%20start%20another%20company.%20If%20you%20do%20it%20right%20once%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-tech-job-launch-startup-now-make-400000-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714381501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662bf39d0dfb1341e9ffcf04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-tech-job-launch-startup-now-make-400000-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gene%20Caballero%20had%20a%20stable%20job%20at%20Dell%2C%20but%20he%20quit%20to%20c