um%20turnover%2C%20opting%20for%20notional%20turnover%20as%20the%20basis%20entails%20a%20higher%20fee%20outlay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBSE%20is%20hereby%20advised%20to%20pay%20the%20regulatory%20fee%20based%20on%20annual%20turnover%20to%20Sebi%20considering%20the%20notional%20value%20in%20case%20of%20options%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20exchange%20said%20in%20a%20filing%20to%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE)%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20exchange%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20pay%20the%20differential%20regulatory%20fee%20for%20the%20past%20periods%20along%20with%20an%20interest%20of%2015%20per%20cent%20per%20annum%20on%20the%20remaining%20unpaid%20amount.%20It%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20pay%20the%20amount%20within%20one%20month%20of%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20filing%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebi's%20letter%20mentioned%20that%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20derivative%20contracts%2C%20BSE%20has%20been%20paying%20the%20regulatory%20fee%20on%20%26quot%3Bannual%20turnover%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20regulator%20considering%20premium%20value%20for%20option%20contracts%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20notional%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20disclosure%20on%20Sunday%2C%20BSE%20said%20it%20is%20currently%20evaluating%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20claim%20as%20per%20Sebi%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20it%20is%20ascertained%20that%20the%20said%20amount%20is%20payable%2C%20the%20total%20differential%20Sebi%20regulatory%20fees%20for%20the%20period%20from%20FY%202006-07%20to%20FY%202022-23%20would%20be%20Rs%2068.64%20crore%20plus%20GST%2C%20which%20includes%20an%20interest%20of%20Rs%2030.34%20crore.%20Further%2C%20the%20differential%20Sebi%20regulatory%20fees%20for%20FY%202023-24%2C%20if%20liable%2C%20could%20be%20around%20Rs%2096.30%20crore%20plus%20GST%2C%20BSE%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20watchdog%20had%20introduced%20the%20regulatory%20fee%20on%20recognised%20stock%20exchanges%20under%20the%20Sebi%20(Regulatory%20Fee%20on%20Stock%20Exchanges)%20Regulations%202006%2C%20whereby%20the%20exchanges%20are%20required%20to%20pay%20the%20fee%20to%20the%20board%20within%2030%20days%20of%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20financial%20year.%20The%20rate%20of%20regulatory%20fee%20was%20based%20on%20the%20annual%20turnover%20of%20the%20stock%20exchanges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714381080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Fbjkfotl8_sensex-nifty-reuters_625x300_31_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-markets-fall-19-after-sebis-new-directive-on-regulatory-fee-5548239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leading%20stock%20exchange%20BSE%20is%20expected%20to%20shell%20out%20more%20regulatory%20fee%20after%20the%20markets%20watchdog%20Sebi%20asked%20the%20bourse%20to%20pay%20the%20fee%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bnotional%20value%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20options%20contracts%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20premium%20value.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-markets-fall-19-after-sebis-new-directive-on-regulatory-fee-5548239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-markets-fall-19-after-sebis-new-directive-on-regulatory-fee-5548239%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-markets-fall-19-after-sebis-new-directive-on-regulatory-fee-5548239%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20wanna%20kill'%3A%20Police%20allege%20teenagers%20plotted%20attack%20days%20after%20Sydney%20church%20stabbing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714380960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%