-scale%20manufacturers'%20profits%20dipped%203.5%25%20in%20March%20compared%20with%20a%20year%20earlier.%20For%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20profits%20were%20up%204.3%25%20to%201.51%20trillion%20yuan%2C%20or%20about%20%24208%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20data%20highlights%20how%20weak%20domestic%20demand%20is%20eating%20into%20Chinese%20manufacturers'%20profits%2C%20causing%20companies%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-overcapacity-dumping-manufacturing-exports-economic-woes-world-yellen-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esell%20products%20en%20masse%20overseas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Janet%20Yellen%2C%20the%20US%20treasury%20secretary%2C%20and%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20state%2C%20visited%20China%20in%20the%20past%20month%2C%20where%20they%20warned%20of%20Chinese%20companies%20undercutting%20other%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlinken%20said%20at%20a%20Friday%20press%20conference%20that%20he%20talked%20with%20Chinese%20officials%20about%20overcapacity%20in%20key%20industries%2C%20including%20solar%20panels%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20alone%20is%20producing%20more%20than%20100%25%20of%20global%20demand%20for%20these%20products%2C%20flooding%20markets%2C%20undermining%20competition%2C%20and%20putting%20at%20risk%20livelihoods%20and%20businesses%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20real%20train%20wreck%20coming'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20area%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20US%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-crush-tesla-elon-musk-american-ev-industry-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotecting%20domestic%20car%20production%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20though%20Chinese%20car%20companies%20don't%20sell%20cars%20in%20many%20large%20markets%2C%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20Chinese%20automakers'%20overall%20profit%20jumped%2032%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20year%20on%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20needs%20to%20expand%20into%20new%20markets%20for%20many%20goods%20because%20domestic%20appetite%20has%20risen%20much%20slower%20than%20manufacturing%20output.%20Last%20year%2C%20China%20and%20Japan%20were%20neck%20and%20neck%20for%20the%20title%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20auto%20exporter%2C%20and%20the%20Chinese%20EV%20maker%20BYD%20outsold%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-04-02%2Fus-europe-gripes-on-china-overcapacity-aren-t-all-backed-by-data%3Fsrnd%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20so%20far%2C%20increased%20EV%20production%20hadn't%20led%20to%20a%20big%20uptick%20in%20inventory%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20overproduction%20hurting%20other%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20cars%20weren't%20the%20only%20bright%20spot%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%3A%20Electronic%20industry%20profits%20were%20up%2082.5%25%20year%20on%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20NBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Froman%2C%20the%20US%20trade%20representative%20during%20the%20Obama%20administration%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F04%2F25%2Fcfrs-michael-froman-on-trade-conflict-with-china-theres-a-real-train-wreck-coming-here.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20China's%20export-led%20growth%20had%20come%20just%20as%20international%20markets%20were%20closing%20to%20the%20country.%20China%20has%20publicly%20written%20off%20US%20warnings%20about%20overproduction%20as%20posturing%20ahead%20of%20the%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20real%20train%20wreck%20coming%20here%20where%20this%20is%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20trade%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Froman%2C%20who's%20now%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20broader%20than%20election-year%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBS%20analyst%20Yu%20Weining%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20accompanying%20Saturday's%20data%20release%20that%20China%20was%20focused%20on%20boosting%20domestic%20demand%20and%20improving%20business%20confidence.%20Overall%2C%20domestic%20demand%20is%20depressed%20as%20the%20country%20faces%20a%20faltering%20GDP%20and%20a%20roiling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevergrande-ordered-liquidate-china-real-estate-property-crisis-winners-assets-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproperty%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-manufacturers-profits-dip-carmakers-surge-us-concern-overproduction-factory-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714380163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f437dec0c696569fe89e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-manufacturers-profits-dip-carmakers-surge-us-concern-overproduction-factory-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weak%20domestic%20demand%20is%20causing%20Chinese%20companies%20to%20sell%20products%20en%20masse%20overseas%2C%20worrying%20US%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meghan%20Morris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-manufacturers-profits-dip-carmakers-surge-us-concern-overproduction-factory-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korea's%20president%20talks%20to%20opposition%20about%20cooperation%20after%20his%20party%20was%20routed%20in%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714380116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fms