0Friction%20With%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20as%20the%20Philippines%20continues%20to%20manage%20a%20maritime%20territorial%20dispute%20with%20Beijing%2C%20the%20friction%20between%20India%20and%20China%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20is%20set%20to%20enter%20its%20fifth%20year%20in%20May.%20The%20tensions%20have%20virtually%20led%20to%20the%20stalling%20of%20the%20boundary%20talks%20involving%20special%20representatives%20from%20the%20two%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20thus%2C%20is%20a%20clear%20'common%20cause'%20as%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20step%20up%20their%20military%20engagement.%20With%20a%20change%20in%20leadership%20from%20the%20China-leaning%20Rodrigo%20Duterte%20to%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20Jr%2C%20who%20believes%20in%20forging%20closer%20ties%20with%20the%20US%2C%20the%20timing%20is%20also%20just%20right%20for%20India%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Focus%20Long%20Due%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20had%20a%20'Look%20East'%20policy%20since%201991%2C%20which%20was%20later%20renamed%20%26quot%3BAct%20East%26quot%3B%20in%202014.%20Both%20policies%20were%20a%20diplomatic%20effort%20to%20develop%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20security%20cooperation%20with%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20engagement%20with%20the%20Philippines%20has%20been%20rather%20underwhelming.%20But%20things%20seem%20to%20be%20improving%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20ASEAN%20level%2C%20the%20defence%20mechanism%20includes%20a%20Defence%20Ministers'%20Meeting%20(ADMM)-Plus%2C%20which%20India%20participates%20in.%20The%20ADMM%20is%20the%20highest%20defence%20consultative%20and%20cooperative%20mechanism%20in%20the%20grouping.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20India's%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20attended%20the%2010th%20ADMM-Plus%20meeting%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20Indonesia.%20He%20expressed%20India's%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20freedom%20of%