r%20to%20Hamas%2C%20which%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%2054%20days%20of%20captivity%20for%20her.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20she%20was%20moved%20to%207%20different%20locations%2C%20quickly%20adapting%20to%20different%20survival%20strategies.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20need%20to%20protect%20your%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained%20to%20the%20BBC.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20in%20the%20first%20house%20stays%20there%2C%20and%20doesn't%20come%20with%20you%20to%20the%20second%20house%20%5Bor%5D%20the%20third%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Ms%20Yanai%20was%20held%20with%20another%20woman%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20who%20was%20taken%20while%20she%20was%20barefoot%20and%20in%20her%20pajamas.%20Ms%20Yanai%20overheard%20their%20captors%20discussing%20who%20would%20marry%20the%20woman%20and%20recalled%20a%20disturbing%20incident%20when%20their%20captors%20brought%20in%20the%20younger%20woman's%20mother%2C%20asking%20for%20permission%20to%20marry%20her%20daughter.%20This%2018-year-old%20woman%20is%20presumed%20to%20be%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-year-old-freed-israeli-hostage-reveals-hamas-captor-wanted-to-marry-her-5527195%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520she%2520added.-%2CNoga%2520Weiss%2520was%2520at%2520home%2520in%2520Kibbutz%2520Be'eri%2520when%2Cbody%2520was%2520taken%2520into%2520Gaza.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-year-old-freed-israeli-hostage-reveals-hamas-captor-wanted-to-marry-her-5527195%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520she%2520added.-%2CNoga%2520Weiss%2520was%2520at%2520home%2520in%2520Kibbutz%2520Be%2527eri%2520when%2Cbody%2520was%2520taken%2520into%2520Gaza.%5C%22%3ENoga%20Weiss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20recently%20recounted%20her%2050-day%20captivity%20period%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Yanai%20shared%20that%20she%20herself%20was%20not%20sexually%20assaulted%20during%20her%20captivity%2C%20but%20she%20learned%20from%20other%20female%20hostages%20that%20they%20had%20been%20raped%20while%20in%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20the%20unsettling%20process%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bexamined%26quot%3B%20when%20moving%20between%20houses%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20'really%20necessary%20test'%20as%20they%20explain%20it%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20always%20try%20to%20explain%20to%20people%20that%20'rape'%20is%20a%20really%20big%20word.%20It's%20not%20only%20the%20act.%20Even%20when%20a%20guy%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20your%20door%2C%20and%20you're%20sitting%20down%2C%20and%20he's%20staring%20at%20you%20for%2010%20minutes%20straight%2C%20five%20to%20six%20times%20a%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20for%2054%20days.%20Trust%20me%3B%20that's%20a%20rape.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recounted%20how%20one%20day%2C%20she%20and%20the%20other%20hostages%20had%20to%20play%20cards%20with%20their%20captors%20to%20try%20to%20get%20something%20to%20eat%20because%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cso%20hungry%E2%80%9D.%20Ms%20Yanai%20tried%20to%20make%20them%20laugh%20with%20jokes.%20But%20one%20captor%20got%20angry%20and%20pointed%20a%20gun%20at%20her%20head%2C%20threatening%20to%20kill%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoran%20Stella%20Yanai%20was%20released%20after%2054%20days%20on%20November%2029%20as%20part%20of%20a%20temporary%20ceasefire%20agreement%20facilitated%20by%20Qatar%20and%20the%20United%20States%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714378080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fn4bfmb7g_music-fest-survivor_625x300_29_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-hostage-moran-stella-yanai-s-harrowing-testimony-of-her-54-days-captivity-in-gaza-5547776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moran%20Stella%20Yanai%20went%20through%20a%20harrowing%20experience%20during%20her%2054-day%20captivity%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20the%2040-year-old%2