%20naked%20atop%20the%20sand%20dune%20have%20gone%20massively%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20sickening%20and%20it%20really%20creates%20a%20bad%20image%20for%20Namibia%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenneth%20Nependa%2C%20vice-chairperson%20of%20the%20Federation%20of%20Namibian%20Tourism%20Associations%2C%20told%20the%20Namibian%20Sun.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20Big%20Daddy%20dune%20was%20not%20just%20a%20relaxing%20place%20for%20tourists%20but%20for%20families%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomeo%20Muyunda%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20ministry%20of%20environment%2C%20forestry%20and%20tourism%2C%20termed%20the%20behaviour%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20shocking%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20public%20indecency%20punishable%20by%20Namibian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20appeal%20to%20that%20section%20of%20tourists%20to%20summon%20the%20conscience%20so%20that%20they%20do%20the%20right%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Muyunda%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20tourists%20had%20left%20Namibia%20by%20the%20time%20the%20authorities%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tourists'%20conduct%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20social%20media%20with%20some%20people%20criticising%20them%20while%20others%20saying%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20wrong%20with%20sunbathing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sossusvlei.org%2Fattractions%2Fbig-daddy%2F%5C%22%3Eofficial%20website%20of%20the%20dune%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Big%20Daddy%20is%20not%20the%20highest%20dune%20in%20the%20Namib%20desert.%20This%20honour%20is%20given%20to%20Dune%207%2C%20which%20has%20been%20measured%20at%20388%20metres.%20%C2%A0Dune%207%20earned%20its%20name%20by%20being%20the%207th%20dune%20along%20the%20Tsauchab%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714375500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Felqnm40o_big-daddy-dune-namibia-1200_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnamibia-slam-tourists-who-posed-naked-on-popular-sand-dune-sickening-5547568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Namibian%20government%20official%20said%20that%20the%20tourists%20had%20left%20Namibia%20by%20the%20time%20the%20authorities%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnamibia-slam-tourists-who-posed-naked-on-popular-sand-dune-sickening-5547568%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnamibia-slam-tourists-who-posed-naked-on-popular-sand-dune-sickening-5547568%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnamibia-slam-tourists-who-posed-naked-on-popular-sand-dune-sickening-5547568%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjeeda%3A%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20fabulous%20a%20dancer%20till%20I%20met%20SLB%20sir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714375318000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109684927%2Cimgsize-34436.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsanjeeda-sheikh-i-thought-i-was-fabulous-dancer-till-i-met-sanjay-leela-bhansali-sir-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F109685008.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109685008.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESanjeeda%20Sheikh%2C%20known%20for%20her%20dancing%20skills%2C%20shared%20her%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali%20on%20his%20OTT%20debut%2C%20%26quot%3BHeeramandi%3A%20The%20Diamond%20Market.%26quot%3B%20She%20praised%20Bhansali's%20passion%20for%20music%20and%20dance%2C%20admitting%20that%20his%20feedback%20made%20her%20a%20better%20performer.%20Sanjeeda%20feels%20blessed%20to%20work%20with%20Bhansali%20and%20his%20star-studded%20cast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jigar%20Shah%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pro-Khalistan%20Slogans%20Raised%20In%20Presence%20Of%20Canada%20PM%20On%20Khalsa%20Day%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Khalsa%20Day%20Celebrations%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Toronto%2C%20loud%20chants%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20slogans%20were%20seen%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20as%20well%20as%20opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre.%20This%20comes%20amid%20a%20rise%20in%20anti-India%20sentiment%20in%20Canada%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20PM%20Trudeau%20was%20about%20to%20take%20the%20stage%20for%20his%20address%20to%20mark%20Khalsa%20Day%2C%20the%20chants%20were%20heard%20getting%20louder%20till%20he%20arrives%20and%20commences%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20video%20released%20by%20Canada-based%20CPAC%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlogans%20of%20%26quot%3BKhalistan%20Zindabad%26quot%3B%20were%20heard%20at%20the%20event%20in%20which%2C%20NDP%20Leader%20Jagmeet%20Singh%20and%20Toronto%20Mayor%20Olivia%20Chow%20were%20also%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20instance%20also%20occurred%20when%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20official%20opposition%20of%20Canada%2C%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20stage%20to%20begin%20his%20address%20to%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20reached%20downtown%20Toronto%20on%20Sunday%20for%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20yearly%20gatherings%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ontario%20Sikhs%20and%20Gurdwaras%20Council%20(OSGC)%2C%20Vaisakhi%2C%20also%20called%20Khalsa%20Day%2C%20commemorates%20the%20founding%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20in%201699%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Sikh%20New%20Year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20has%20been%20organising%20an%20annual%20parade%20down%20Lake%20Shore%20Boulevard%20for%20many%20years%3B%20the%20council%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20the%20third-largest%20parade%20in%20the%20nation%20and%20that%20it%20regularly%20draws%20thousands%20of%20spectators%2C%20according%20to%20CBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20walked%20up%20to%20address%20the%20Sikh%20Community%20in%20Toronto%20loud%20pro-Khalistan%20slogans%20were%20raised%20from%20the%20crowd.%20Trudeau%20in%20a%20staunch%20assurance%20to%20the%20Sikh%20Community%20in%20the%20country%20has%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20always%20there%20to%20protect%20their%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20at%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDiversity%20is%20one%20of%20Canada's%20greatest%20strengths%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20strong%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20differences%2C%20but%20because%20of%20those%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20Canada's%20greatest%20strengths%20is%20its%20diversity.%20We%20are%20strong%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20our%20differences%2C%20but%20because%20of%20our%20differences%3B%20but%20even%20as%20we%20look%20at%20these%20differences%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remember%2C%20and%20get%20reminded%20on%20days%20such%20as%20this%2C%20and%20every%20day%2C%20that%20Sikh%20values%20are%20Canadian%20values...%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said%20during%20the%20Khalsa%20Day%20Celebrations%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20nearly%2C%20800%2C000%20Canadians%20of%20Sikh%20heritage%20across%20this%20country%2C%20we%20will%20always%20be%20there%20to%20protect%20your%20rights%20and%20your%20freedoms%2C%20and%20we%20will%20always%20defend%20your%20community%20against%20hatred%20and%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20PM%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20country%20is%20enhancing%20the%20security%20and%20infrastructure%20programmes%20by%20%26quot%3Badding%20more%20security%20at%20community%20centres%20and%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20including%20Gurdwaras.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20right%20to%20practice%20your%20religion%20freely%2C%20and%20without%20intimidation%20is%20exactly%20that.%20A%20fundamental%20right%20guaranteed%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Charter%20of%20Rights%20and%20Freedoms%20that%20we%20will%20always%20stand%20up%20and%20defend%20you%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20assured%20the%20Sikh%20community%20in%20his%20Khalsa%20Day%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trudeau's%20remarks%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20are%20going%20through%20a%20difficult%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20notably%2C%20the%20killing%20of%20India-designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20that%20sparked%20a%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20as%20he%20came%20out%20of%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20his%20killing%20that%20reportedly%20surfaced%20in%20March%20recently%2C%20showed%20Nijjar%20being%20shot%20by%20armed%20men%20in%20what%20has%20been%20described%20as%20a%20'contract%20killing'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20led%20to%20accusations%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20killing%20--%20a%20claim%20that%20was%20denied%20by%20India%20and%20led%20to%20the%20deterioration%20of%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20Canada%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%2