%20million%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDubai%20is%20undertaking%20a%20massive%20expansion%20of%20an%20airport%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20be%20five%20times%20the%20size%20of%20its%20current%20international%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsheikh-mohammed-bin-rashid-al-maktoum-emir-dubai-2019-7%23sheikh-mohammed-bin-rashid-al-maktoum-was-born-on-july-15-1949-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Mohammed%20bin%20Rashid%20Al%20Maktoum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20emirate's%20ruler%2C%20said%20the%20upgraded%20Al%20Maktoum%20International%20Airport%20will%20feature%20a%20capacity%20of%20260%20million%20passengers%2C%20the%20world's%20largest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20building%20a%20new%20project%20for%20future%20generations%2C%20ensuring%20continuous%20and%20stable%20development%20for%20our%20children%20and%20their%20children%20in%20turn%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHHShkMohd%2Fstatus%2F1784485931275149431%2Fphoto%2F3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BDubai%20will%20be%20the%20world's%20airport%2C%20its%20port%2C%20its%20urban%20hub%2C%20and%20its%20new%20global%20center.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20the%20world's%20busiest%20airport%20in%202023%2C%20the%20Hartfield-Jackson%20Atlanta%20International%20Airport%2C%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FATL-ATR-2312.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E104.6%20million%20passengers%20that%20year.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20international%20flights%20now%20operate%20out%20of%20Dubai%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20some%2087%20million%20passengers%20visited%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20operations%20there%20will%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20Al%20Maktoum%20facility%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20host%20five%20parallel%20runways%20and%20400%20aircr