2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-town-building-barrier-stop-tourists-taking-mount-fuji-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeloved%20tourist%20spot%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20weak%20currency%20is%20ensuring%20that%20it%20will%20remain%20that%20way%20for%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20just%20broke%20its%20pre-pandemic%20tourist%20record%2C%20with%203.1%20million%20foreign%20visitors%20in%20March.%20The%20government%20said%20it's%20on%20track%20to%20surpass%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japantimes.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2F17%2Fjapan%2Fsociety%2Frecord-high-inbound-travelers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025's%20target%20of%2032%20million%20annual%20foreign%20visitors%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20after%208.6%20million%20tourists%20visited%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20opened%20to%20tourists%20in%20October%202022%2C%20after%20over%20two%20years%20of%20strict%2C%20pandemic-induced%20border%20restrictions.%20Pent-up%20demand%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20cheaper%20currency%2C%20has%20fueled%20the%20record%20number%20of%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETourists%20are%20staying%20longer%20and%20spending%20more%20due%20to%20the%20weak%20yen%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20cheaper%20for%20foreigners%20to%20purchase%20accommodation%2C%20activities%2C%20food%2C%20and%20gifts.%20The%20yen%20has%20fallen%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fjpy-usd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10%25%20year-to-date%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20currency%20has%20been%20depreciating%20largely%20due%20to%20high%20interest%20rates%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20dollar%20more%20attractive%20to%20investors.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-central-bank-raises-interest-rates-17-years-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20rate%20hike%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Japan%20last%20month%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20first%20since%202007%20%E2%80%94%20did%20little%20to%20reverse%20the%20downward%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20a%20tourist%20hot%20spot%20because%20of%20its%20status%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcenturies-old-japanese-ceramics-maker-maruwa-ai-revolution-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20entertainment%20icon%2C%20its%20natural%20wonders%2C%20and%20its%20unique%20cuisine.%20Tourists%20from%20South%20Korea%2C%20China%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20the%20US%20made%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.jnto.go.jp%2Fen%2Fgraph%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20portion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20foreign%20visitors%20in%20March%2C%20according%20to%20Japan's%20National%20Tourism%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapanese%20carriers%20like%20Japan%20Airlines%20and%20ANA%20plan%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20tourism%20boom%20by%20running%20more%20routes%20from%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sharp%20decline%20of%20the%20yen%20has%20also%20expanded%20demand%20for%20luxury%20goods.%20Foreign%20tourists%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20currency%20discount%20by%20snapping%20up%20cheaper%20products%20in%20Japan%20from%20premium%20brands%20such%20as%20Swiss%20watchmaker%20TAG%20Heuer%2C%20Chanel%2C%20and%20Prada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-04-17%2Fhow-to-get-cheaper-luxury-goods-japan-s-weak-yen-provides-bargains%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20weak%20yen%20creates%20a%20sweet%20spot%20for%20foreigners%2C%20it%20is%20severely%20hurting%20Japanese%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20outbound%20travelers%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.jnto.go.jp%2Fen%2Fgraph%2F%23graph--latest--figures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20than%20half%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20number%20of%20inbound%20travelers%20in%20March%2C%20per%20the%20National%20Tourism%20Organization.%20Outbound%20Japanese%20travel%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.jnto.go.jp%2Fen%2Fgraph%2F%23graph--latest--figures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edown%2037%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20in%202019%2C%20though%20it%20ticked%20up%20from%20February%2C%20the%20agency's%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20airfare%20costs%20and%20low%20buying%20power%20is%20compelling%20more%20locals%20to%20skip%20international%20travel%20in%20favor%20of%20domestic%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-weak-currency-yen-boosts-foreign-tourism-luxury-purchases-travel-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714369207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f126eec0c696569fe885d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-weak-currency-yen-boosts-foreign-tourism-luxury-purchases-travel-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tourists%20are%20staying%20longer%20and%20spending%20more%20as%20the%20yen%20continues%20its%20slide%20against%20the%20dollar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-weak-currency-yen-boosts-foreign-tourism-luxury-purchases-travel-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2220%25%20Type%202%20Diabetes%20Cases%20Linked%20To%20Air%20Pollution%2C%20Says%20Lancet%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProlonged%20exposure%20to%20polluted%20air%20with%20PM%202.5%20particulate%20matter%2C%20which%20is%2030%20times%20thinner%20than%20a%20strand%20of%20hair%2C%20can%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20a%20new%20study%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20Lancet%2C%20a%20leading%20medical%20journal%2C%20outlines%20how%2020%25%20of%20type%202%20diabetes%20is%20linked%20to%20chronic%20exposure%20to%20PM%202.5%20pollutants.%20These%20fine%20pollutants%20are%20emitted%20from%20oil%2C%20diesel%2C%20biomass%2C%20and%20gasoline%20combustion.%20The%20study%20has%20wider%20implications%20in%20India%20due%20to%20increasing%20pollution%20and%20exposure%20of%20a%20large%20population%20to%20harmful%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lancet%20Study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%202.5%20pollutant%20is%20often%20termed%20as%20a%20killer%20and%20is%20a%20major%20component%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20urban%20areas.%20The%20study%20suggests%20that%20short-term%20exposure%20to%20PM%202.5%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20insulin%20resistance%20by%20triggering%20the%20autonomic%20nervous%20system%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pathway%20toward%20cardiovascular%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20a%20monthly%20exposure%20to%20PM%202.5%20pollutants%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20and%20a%20prolonged%20exposure%20(almost%20a%20year)%20led%20to%20a%2020%25%20increase%20in%20risk%20of%20type%202%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20link%20between%20air%20pollution%20and%20diabetes%20is%20higher%20in%20men%20groups%20from%20lower%20socioeconomic%20groups%20and%20those%20with%20comorbidities.%20Evidence%20suggests%20that%20PM2.5%20is%20associated%20with%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%20in%20populations%20both%20with%20and%20without%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20537%20million%20suffer%20from%20type%202%20diabetes%20and%20half%20of%20them%20are%20unaware%20that%20they%20are%20diabetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20India%2C%20an%20estimated%2077%20million%20people%20above%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20are%20suffering%20from%20diabetes%20(type%202)%20and%20nearly%2025%20million%20are%20prediabetics%20(at%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20developing%20diabetes%20in%20the%20future)%2C%20according%20to%20WHO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolluted%20Air%20In%20Indian%20Cities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-worlds-most-polluted-capital-city-again-report-5265746%5C%22%3EBihar's%20Begusarai%20emerged%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20polluted%20metropolitan%20area%20while%20Delhi%20was%20identified%20as%20the%20capital%20city%20with%20the%20poorest%20air%20quality%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report.%20The%20national%20capital%20has%20ranked%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital%20city%20in%20the%20world%20four%20times%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20average%20annual%20PM2.5%20concentration%20of%2054.4%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%2C%20India%20had%20the%20third%20worst%20air%20quality%20out%20of%20134%20countries%20in%202023%20after%20Bangladesh%20(79.9%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre)%20and%20Pakistan%20(73.7%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report%202023%20by%20Swiss%20organisation%20IQAir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20India%20was%20ranked%20as%20the%20eighth%20most%20polluted%20country%20with%20an%20average%20PM2.5%20concentration%20of%2053.3%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%201.36%20billion%20people%20in%20India%20experience%20PM2.5%20concentrations%20exceeding%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20recommended%20annual%20guideline%20level%20of%205%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-%20With%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714369080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F259tq5g8_delhi-air-pollution-pti_625x300_03_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fi