%20Indian%20Boxing%20Team%20preparing%20for%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharat%20and%20Shaaswat%20swam%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348060%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBharat%20and%20Shaaswat%20swam%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaaswat%20Sharma%20(31)%2C%20a%20technical%20architect%2C%20is%20an%20ultra%20long-distance%20swimmer%2C%20triathlete%2C%20national%20water%20polo%20player%2C%20and%20swimmer.%20He%20holds%20all%20India%20records%20and