swat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20was%20very%20choppy%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20swim%2C%20unlike%20the%20condition%20they%20had%20practised%20in.%20Yet%2C%20the%20two%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20anything%20deter%20them%20that%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20can%20lose%20your%20breath%20and%20composure.%20The%20water%20can%20be%20very%20unforgiving.%20You%20face%20certain%20life%20and%20death%20moments%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20that%20you%20must%20respect%20the%20process.%20Take%20the%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20hours%20were%20excruciating%2C%20their%20skin%20was%20completely%20burnt%2C%20the%20water%20rough%2C%20and%20their%20energy%20low.%20They%20kept%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20their%20goal%20for%20doing%20this%20swim.%20The%20crew%20also%20kept%20cheering%20and%20motivating%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20navigate%20the%20turbulent%20waters.%20It%20was%20a%20test%20of%20their%20mental%20and%20emotional%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20this%20achievement%20has%20a%20very%20high%20spiritual%20and%20cultural%20significance.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333570%2Fsachin-nag-won-only-gold-medal-swimming-for-india-at-asian-games-sports-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20swimmer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20participated%20in%20several%20challenges%2C%20but%20crossing%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20is%20one%20for%20the%20country.%20While%20we%20were%20swimming%20the%20stretch%2C%20we%20were%20filled%20with%20mixed%20emotions%2C%20of%20celebrating%20the%20spirit%20of%20universal%20brotherhood%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20calling%20out%20to%20the%20nation%20to%20nurture%20swimming%20as%20a%20key%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2F