ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2Falphonso-768x402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-257956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20Noorjahan%20mango%20can%20grow%20up%20to%20a%20foot%20long.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20history%20points%20to%20the%20Mughal%20beneficence%20towards%20the%20development%20of%20different%20mango%20varieties%2C%20the%20Noorjahan%E2%80%99s%20naming%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20Mughal%20queen%20by%20way%20of%20its%20descriptor%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Emallika-e-aam%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20queen%20of%20mangoes%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20%3Cem%3ECNN%20traveller%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20says.%20The%20mangoes%20can%20weigh%20up%20to%203.5%20kg%20and%20can%20grow%20up%20to%20a%20foot-long%20in%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoveted%20among%20mango%20lovers%2C%20its%20restricted%20production%20makes%20it%20rare%20and%20is%20only%20consumed%20in%20Gujarat.%20Depending%20on%20the%20size%20and%20season%2C%20the%20price%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20piece.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%C2%A0%20Miyazaki%20Mango%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrown%20typically%20in%20Japan%2C%20this%20mango%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20mango%20costing%20up%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%2Fkg%20in%20the%20international%20markets.%20These%20mangoes%20are%20grown%20in%20the%20Miyazaki%20Prefecture%20of%20Japan%20and%20are%20highly%20prized%20for%20their%20deep%20red%20skin%20and%20sweet%2C%20rich%20flavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fred-1713795919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miyazaki%20Mango%20is%20typically%20grown%20in%20Japan.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri