ensive%2C%20and%20have%20distinctive%20taste.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347996%2Frare-mangoes-available-in-india-alphonso-sindhri-mango-expensive-mangoes-summer-season%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Idli%20Places%20in%20Bengaluru%20Which%20Serve%20Extra%20Love%20For%20%E2%80%98Thatte%20Idlis%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReminiscent%20of%20a%20flat%20disc%20or%20plate%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ethatte%20idli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20steamed%20rice%20and%20lentil%20cake)%20is%20larger%20than%20the%20usual%20variants%20of%20this%20cult%20favourite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309836%2Ffood-history-of-idli-sambar-roots-in-indonesia-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Indian%20breakfast%20%3C%2Fa%3Edish.%20The%20%E2%80%98cloud-like%E2%80%99%20texture%20of%20these%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20lent%20by%20the%20ground%20tapioca%20pearls%20that%20go%20into%20the%20batter.%20With%20a%20side%20of%20hand-churned%20butter%20and%20spicy%20coconut%20chutney%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ethatte%20idli%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20ultimate%20crowd-puller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20article%2C%20we%20explore%20heritage%20restaurants%20and%20local%20spots%20that%20dish%20up%20this%20popular%20snack%20as%20well%20as%20famous%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ejoints%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Veena%20Stores%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20put%20out%20by%20food%20and%20travel%20platform%20%3Cem%3ECurly%20Tales%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bollywood%20icon%20Deepika%20Padukone%20declared%20her%20love%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20served%20at%20Veena%20Stores%20in%20Malleshwaram.%20Started%20in%201977%2C%20the%20eatery%20has%20been%20thrilling%20its%20customers